fields.customfield_12215: /HGW/Webui/Common/My WiFi/Advanced WiFi/Different configuration for WiFi 5GHz and WiFi 2.4 GHz

fields.Action: From the WebUI, try to Switch OFF the WiFi on 2.4Ghz band.
fields.Expected Result:
It should be possible to switch OFF the Wifi on 2.4Ghz band.
The SSID should be no more visible on 2.4Ghz
"Use a tool like InSSider to confirm"

fields.Action: From the WebUI, try to Switch ON the WiFi on 2.4Ghz band.
fields.Expected Result:
It should be possible to switch ON the Wifi on 2.4Ghz band.
The SSID is visible on 2.4Ghz

"Confirm that is working by connecting a station to with and verifiyng connectivity"

fields.description:
The test aims to check the ability to Switch WiFi on and off using the WebUI
 

[Precondition]

Wifi is Active

Same configuration for 2.4 and 5 ghz is choosen from the Webui
